    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>This pattern allows you to adjust the input normals. Occasionally there's an issue where normals pointing away in a bump map introduce artifacts like cracks and black spaces. This node allows you to correct this when using <em>your own</em> bump nodes. </p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"d02d728e-37d5-4b18-9186-f39472e07951\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>We include a parameter for this in <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542222840/PxrBump\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222840\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrBump</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542224317/PxrNormalMap\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224317\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrNormalMap</a> as an out-of-the-box solution.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"PxrAdjustNormal-InputParameters\">Input Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrAdjustNormal-InputNormal\">Input Normal</h4><p>Connect your normal pattern or textures to adjust.</p><h4 id=\"PxrAdjustNormal-AdjustAmount\">Adjust Amount</h4><p>Amount to adjust the normals when the geometric normals are facing away from the camera. This is useful when we see artifacts in the render. The below example is an extreme bump setting designed to exaggerate the effect. Notice that the edges (glancing angles) are most affected. More subtle bumps will see this correction further confined to edges.</p><p>Hover over the image to see the effect.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"adjustNormals_0.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/adjustNormals_0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222488/adjustNormals_0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222516\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"adjustNormals_0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542222488\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"13acde9c-8c1c-4d84-9271-5f4fded19f67\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/adjustNormals_0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/adjustNormals_0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590053&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"adjustNormals_1.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/adjustNormals_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590052&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222488/adjustNormals_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590052&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222513\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"adjustNormals_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542222488\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"059f0b61-6f20-41b9-8c6d-b13e828a3915\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/adjustNormals_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590052&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/adjustNormals_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330590052&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrAdjustNormal-SurfaceNormalMix\">Surface Normal Mix</h4><p>The amount to mix the resulting normals with the original surface normals. Toward 1.0 will mix in more surface normals. In the example below you can see that the original object had no other normals defined and becomes smooth at setting 1.0</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"surfaceNormalMix_00.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589820&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589820&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222510\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"surfaceNormalMix_00.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542222488\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c17a49a5-b3a7-489b-bfb6-7fbe5cb7dc80\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589820&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589820&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"surfaceNormalMix_05.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222504\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"surfaceNormalMix_05.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542222488\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ff80711d-812c-417b-8f7c-d52ea8541b2e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"surfaceNormalMix_10.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222507\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"surfaceNormalMix_10.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542222488\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0cb8de2c-f993-44a9-9d93-709ebd36f260\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542222488/surfaceNormalMix_10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330589819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
